DATABASE
	1. install postgre sql
		install using "https://www.digitalocean.com/community/tutorials/how-to-install-and-use-postgresql-on-ubuntu-18-04"

	2. install pgadmin 
		install using "https://tecadmin.net/install-pgadmin4-on-ubuntu/"

	3. instal NPM PG to conneck your database
		install using "https://www.npmjs.com/package/pg"

	4. instal NPM MOMENT to Aplly "Date" Postgres
		install using "https://www.npmjs.com/package/moment"

Dependency

	1. "npm init --yes" *Didalam folder eksekusi
	
	2. install express-generator
		instal using "http://expressjs.com/en/starter/generator.html"

	3. instal body-parser
		install using " npm i body-parser --save"

	4. install bootstrap
		install using " npm i bootstrap --save"

	5. install nodemone > digunakan untuk router agar tidak perlu merestart terminal, 
		cara penggunaan > 
		1. install nodemon > " npm install --save-dev nodemon "
		2. tambahkan dev nodemon setelah start > "dev": "nodemon ./bin/www"
		3. panggil menggunakan > " npm run dev"

	6. install express-session
		install using " https://www.npmjs.com/package/express-session "